講啊？<br />\n接收資訊嗰個一定要畀發放資訊嗰個屌架？ <br />\n係咪你細個你老竇教你寫字嗰陣一路教一路屌你老母先教到你呢啲撚樣出嚟？ <br />\n屌你老母臭閪谷鳩氣"},{"pid":"fb5c902759cf581e53174456de15392636e02aac","tid":2307200,"uid":14983,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T04:40:02.000Z","msg":"新聞刺賓"},{"pid":"de61a02064a7b43fe61b1261e415d9ecaa8a593e","tid":2307200,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T04:40:13.000Z","msg":"樓豬接手"},{"pid":"5e4fc3112f6eb4a54743aa684f0f2ed09b78f6c1","tid":2307200,"uid":214644,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T04:40:20.000Z","msg":"無咩特別，睇返無線新聞好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71691a698a920bca3e151273122afd5f0c80ced0","tid":2307200,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a7a3ccf4aa49a620ff95c8d4d09d41d08675048f","tid":2307200,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e75f7c2c9e9a1f6439c6772b3bcd296966152d4f","tid":2307200,"uid":38189,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"001930055d9ee2d329bfe44b81a6ae5c123df24c","tid":2307200,"uid":90615,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T04:37:20.000Z","msg":"你對啲針呀盛呀特別敏感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T04:38:05.000Z","msg":"我都係邦莫生講句公道說話姐"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T04:38:50.000Z","msg":"您同莫生咩關係咁邦佢？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T04:40:24.000Z","msg":"我都係姓莫。"},{"pid":"960f9e9d5005ee2facf6dfc05e9edeb76024ca06","tid":2307200,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fb5c902759cf581e53174456de15392636e02aac","tid":2307200,"uid":14983,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T04:40:02.000Z","msg":"新聞刺賓"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T04:41:42.000Z","msg":"泰食堂下次可唔可以咪撚再請韓賓同BoA，請多幾條女好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":